ce:section.ce:para:
To investigate the application ability of Zn/Co-NCDs in water samples, the concentration of Fe (III) in standard water samples was measured. Table 3
                            showed that the probe has good accuracy. In addition, Fe (III) in tap water was determined by a standard addition recovery experiment (Table 3). The recovery rate of Fe (III) in the water sample was 99.00–103.38%. These results indicated that Zn/Co-NCDs have the potential to analyze Fe (III) in environmental water samples (Table 4
                           ).
